## Final Summary

**E4: Media Pool & Audio Storage** - complete with review fixes applied.

**Two commits pushed:**
1. `5a2aa82` - Initial implementation (27 files, +1950 lines)
2. `fc4bfcd` - Review fixes (7 files, +63/-22 lines)

**Key fixes from review:**
- Pool `init()` now properly awaited before exposing to React tree (persisted sources load correctly)
- File passed directly as Blob to IndexedDB (no triple memory copy)
- MP3 detection uses standard 11-bit sync word instead of hardcoded byte values
- `samplesPerPeak <= 0` guard prevents infinite loop
- Persisted sources get their waveform peaks loaded on mount
- Drag-and-drop uses counter ref to prevent flickering

**Final stats:** 41 test files, 318 tests, lint + format + TypeScript strict all clean.